#### ğŸ² Best "Board Game Cafe" Hack: 1st Place ğŸ¥‡

![Image](https://i.imgur.com/vecokWZ.png)

**Team:** Team Chaos (@Aaron ğŸ‡¬ğŸ‡§, @Dut ğŸ‡§ğŸ‡·)
